    "overview": "Ben Horowitz (a16z) joins Peter Diamandis to analyze the most turbulent week in AI: xAI's executive exodus, the stunning $5B valuation for Ilya Sutskever's SSI (Safe Superintelligence), Apple's deepening AI crisis, and Elon Musk's pivot toward lunar AI data centers. Horowitz provides insider perspective on what the talent movements signal about where the frontier is actually moving.",
